    {
      "text": "Your Real Baby to Love and Care for! \n \nTaking care of a baby is not always easy: bathing, bottle-feeding, changing diapers... But what joy when you see your baby smile! My Baby allows you to discover a marvelous adventure filled with emotion.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
